OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be another dry and warm
OL,6,Fday. There will be some good spells of
OL,7,Fsunshine, but a cloudier period is
OL,8,Fpossible around mid- to late morning.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FIt will stay dry throughout
OL,11,Fthe evening and overnight. Some
OL,12,Fprolonged spells of evening sunshine
OL,13,Fleading to clear spells overnight.
OL,14,
OL,15,CSunday:FIt will be dry and warm with
OL,16,Flengthy sunny spells for much of the
OL,17,Fday, but sunshine turning somewhat
OL,18,Fhazier as cloud spreads south in the
OL,19,Fafternoon and evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
